  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/131781224/c2561/order2/\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0,90,148);\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tClose the door<br />\n\tWhy does the door close? Who closes it? What event is happening which requires the closing of the door?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They closed the door... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) a meeting or interview is going to start<br />\n\t2) a thief <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/sneak\" target=\"_blank\">sneak</a>ed into an empty apartment<br />\n\t3) going into a room to get changed<br />\n\t4) too much noise outside<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tHe closed his tired eyes for a while, then checked the time. Everyone in the office should be gone by now, he thought. He got up and walked around the quiet office. Just as he expected, there was nobody in sight in the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/neuroscience\" target=\"_blank\">neuroscience</a> department. He then peered into the main <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/hallway\" target=\"_blank\">hallway</a>. Complete stillness. He quickly scrambled down the hallway towards the chemistry department. Right after the keypad on the door gave access, he heard noise echoing down the hall. It was too late to turn back. He entered the office and quietly closed the door.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/162340241706/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p724245/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p724245\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727210/\">国外知乎：朋友圈老有人拉仇恨怎么办？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727418/\">逗比组图：山寨版奥巴马和金正恩走红</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727416/\">8岁澳洲女孩网上教烹饪 月入79万</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727258/\">和中学恋人走到现在是怎样一种体验？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727083/\">Quora精选 最萌最机智的5句英文</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727303/\">东京街头，日本爷爷遛了只非洲象龟</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727260/\">冰淇淋狂欢节：各种神奇口味英文怎么说？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p532552/\">免费在线学：CCTalk英语大厅课程表</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p161331/\">新概念英语第一册Lesson 1  Excuse me</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p727229/\">史上最全盘点：希拉里的百变搭配</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://ww